====Noun====
{{en-noun|''plural'' '''[[appendices]]''', ''or, by some considered incorrect,'' '''[[appendixes]]'''}}

# A text added to the end of a book or an article, containing information that is important to but not in the focus of the main text
# {{anatomy}} The [[vermiform appendix]], an inner organ without known use that can become inflamed.

